data.description: I'm pleased to present this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home located on a spacious 0.5 acre lot in the desirable Hampstead neighborhood. What's unique about this area is that it includes a dedicated neighborhood boat ramp, perfect for the avid fisherman or watersports enthusiast. This home is move-in ready and perfect for a growing family. As you enter the front door, you are greeted by an open floor plan with hardwood floors throughout. The living room boasts a gas fireplace, making it the perfect space to relax after a long day on the water. Just off the living room is the formal dining room, perfect for entertaining family and friends to hear tales from your latest fishing expedition.The kitchen has been updated with new countertops, stainless steel appliances and oak cabinets for additional storage and work space. It opens to the family room for an easy flow when hosting gatherings. All 3 bedrooms are nicely sized with large windows allowing an abundance of natural light. The primary suite includes a walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. The additional bedrooms provide flexibility for any needs. Outside you will find a huge private backyard that is spacious enough for kids and pets to play. The oversized 2-car garage provides ample storage for all of your boating gear. Located in Olde Point, this home offers both privacy, water access, and safety.I hope you will come take a look at this fantastic opportunity. With the boat ramp just down the street, you'll have the best of all worlds - small town charm with water access just minutes away. Please call to schedule your private showing today!
